    "title": "PokéAPI",
    "description": "A RESTful API for Pokémon data. This is a consumption-only API (GET only).\nNo authentication required. All resources are fully open and available.\n\n**Fair Use Policy**: Please cache resources locally and be respectful of API usage.",
